<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><title>Pixel Bloom</title><style>:root {
  color-scheme: light;
  --bg: #f5efe2;
  --ink: #1f1c18;
  --panel: #fffaf0;
  --stage: #10131d;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #fff6db, var(--bg) 55%);
  color: var(--ink);
}

#app {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 48px 24px 64px;
}

.intro {
  max-width: 42ch;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.art-card {
  margin: 32px 0;
  padding: 24px;
  border: 2px solid rgba(31, 28, 24, 0.12);
  border-radius: 24px;
  background: var(--panel);
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(87, 55, 22, 0.08);
}

.stage {
  position: relative;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  min-height: 240px;
  margin: 24px 0 16px;
  border-radius: 28px;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #121826, #1a2233 55%, #0b0f17);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.stage::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  width: 190px;
  height: 190px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 162, 102, 0.32), rgba(255, 162, 102, 0) 68%);
  filter: blur(8px);
}

.grid {
  position: relative;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 28px);
  gap: 12px;
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  animation: spin 10s linear infinite;
}

.pixel {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  opacity: 0.9;
  box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  animation: bloom 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.p1 { background: #ff8a5b; animation-delay: 0s; }
.p2 { background: #ffd166; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
.p3 { background: #7bd389; animation-delay: 0.4s; }
.p4 { background: #48bfe3; animation-delay: 0.6s; }
.p5 { background: #8093f1; animation-delay: 0.8s; }
.p6 { background: #f07dea; animation-delay: 1s; }
.p7 { background: #fb6f92; animation-delay: 1.2s; }
.p8 { background: #ffb86c; animation-delay: 1.4s; }
.p9 { background: #9bf6ff; animation-delay: 1.6s; }

.caption {
  margin: 0;
  text-align: center;
  font-style: italic;
}

section {
  margin-top: 28px;
}

@keyframes bloom {
  0%, 100% {
    transform: scale(0.72);
    opacity: 0.45;
  }
  50% {
    transform: scale(1.14);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

@keyframes spin {
  from {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  to {
    transform: rotate(405deg);
  }
}</style></head><body><div id="app"><h1>Pixel Bloom</h1><p class="intro">A small computer-art sketch rendered from a Jo HTML DSL.</p><div class="art-card" id="art"><h2>Rotating Mosaic</h2><div class="stage" aria-hidden="true"><div class="grid"><span class="pixel p1"></span><span class="pixel p2"></span><span class="pixel p3"></span><span class="pixel p4"></span><span class="pixel p5"></span><span class="pixel p6"></span><span class="pixel p7"></span><span class="pixel p8"></span><span class="pixel p9"></span></div></div><p class="caption">Nine glowing tiles bloom on staggered timing while the board turns.</p></div><section id="palette"><h2>Palette</h2><p>Warm paper around the frame, a midnight stage in the center, and ember, mint, coral, and sky colors pulsing inside the grid.</p></section><section id="loop"><h2>Loop</h2><p>The tiles breathe in place while the whole mosaic rotates slowly, so the pattern never settles into the same pose twice.</p></section><section id="notes"><h2>Notes</h2><p>The page keeps the structure readable by moving the animation CSS into <code>pageStyles</code> and using the DSL only for the document tree.</p></section><p>Jump to the <a href="#loop">loop notes</a> or back to the <a href="#art">art board</a></p></div></body></html>
